<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Smart Market - Controle Inteligente de Compras</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css" />
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

        :root {
            --primary: #10b981;
            --primary-dark: #059669;
            --secondary: #3b82f6;
            --secondary-dark: #1e40af;
            --accent: #f59e0b;
            --success: #10b981;
            --warning: #f59e0b;
            --danger: #ef4444;
            --light: #f3f4f6;
            --lighter: #f9fafb;
            --gray: #6b7280;
            --gray-dark: #374151;
            --shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            --shadow-sm: 0 4px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
        }

        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", "Roboto", "Oxygen", "Ubuntu", "Cantarell", sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5f7fa 0%, #c3cfe2 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            color: var(--gray-dark);
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary) 0%, var(--primary-dark) 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 2rem 0;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 100;
        }

        .header-content {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            max-width: 1400px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 2rem;
        }

        .logo {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .logo i { font-size: 2rem; }

        .status-sync {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }

        .status-sync .dot {
            width: 10px;
            height: 10px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: #4ade80;
            animation: pulse 2s infinite;
        }

        @keyframes pulse {
            0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
            50% { opacity: 0.5; }
        }

        nav {
            display: flex;
            gap: 0;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            margin: 1.5rem 0 0 0;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
        }

        .nav-button {
            flex: 1;
            min-width: 150px;
            padding: 1rem;
            background: transparent;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            border-bottom: 3px solid transparent;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
        }

        .nav-button:hover { background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); }

        .nav-button.active {
            border-bottom-color: white;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1400px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 2rem;
        }

        section {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
            display: none;
            animation: fadeIn 0.4s ease-in-out;
        }

        section.active { display: block; }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(10px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }

        section h2 {
            color: var(--primary);
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.75rem;
        }

        section h2 i { font-size: 1.6rem; }

        .dashboard-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .dashboard-card {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.05) 0%, rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.05) 100%);
            border: 2px solid rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.1);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .dashboard-card:hover {
            border-color: var(--primary);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        .dashboard-card h3 {
            color: var(--gray);
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .metric-value {
            font-size: 2.2rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--primary);
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .metric-label {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: var(--gray);
        }

        .chart-container {
            height: 300px;
            position: relative;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        form { display: flex; flex-direction: column; }

        .form-group { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }

        label {
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--gray-dark);
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }

        input, select, textarea {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 0.875rem;
            border: 2px solid var(--light);
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-family: inherit;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            background: white;
        }

        input:focus, select:focus, textarea:focus {
            outline: none;
            border-color: var(--primary);
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.1);
        }

        .form-group-row {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 1rem;
        }

        .items-container {
            background: var(--lighter);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .item {
            background: white;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border-left: 4px solid var(--primary);
            position: relative;
        }

        .item:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }

        .item-header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .item-number {
            background: var(--primary);
            color: white;
            width: 32px;
            height: 32px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        .btn-remove-item {
            background: var(--danger);
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
            border-radius: 6px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .btn-remove-item:hover {
            background: #dc2626;
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }

        button {
            padding: 0.875rem 1.5rem;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 1rem;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary) 0%, var(--primary-dark) 100%);
            color: white;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow);
        }

        .btn-secondary {
            background: var(--light);
            color: var(--gray-dark);
            border: 2px solid var(--secondary);
        }

        .btn-secondary:hover {
            background: var(--secondary);
            color: white;
        }

        .btn-sm {
            padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        .list-container { list-style: none; }

        .list-item {
            background: var(--lighter);
            padding: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border-left: 4px solid var(--secondary);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .list-item:hover {
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
            transform: translateX(4px);
        }

        .list-item-title {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--gray-dark);
        }

        .list-item-value {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--primary);
        }

        .card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .card h3 {
            color: var(--gray-dark);
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }

        table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin-top: 1rem;
        }

        thead { background: var(--light); }

        th {
            padding: 1rem;
            text-align: left;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--gray-dark);
            border-bottom: 2px solid #e5e7eb;
        }

        td {
            padding: 1rem;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }

        tbody tr:hover { background: var(--lighter); }

        .toast {
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 2rem;
            right: 2rem;
            background: white;
            padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 1rem;
            animation: slideIn 0.3s ease;
            z-index: 1001;
        }

        .toast.success { border-left: 4px solid var(--success); }
        .toast.error { border-left: 4px solid var(--danger); }
        .toast.info { border-left: 4px solid var(--secondary); }

        @keyframes slideIn {
            from { transform: translateX(400px); opacity: 0; }
            to { transform: translateX(0); opacity: 1; }
        }

        footer {
            background: var(--gray-dark);
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 2rem;
            margin-top: 4rem;
        }

        footer p { margin: 0.5rem 0; }

        .about-hero {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary) 0%, var(--secondary) 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 3rem 2rem;
            border-radius: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .about-hero h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .about-hero p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            opacity: 0.95;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .features-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .feature-card {
            background: var(--lighter);
            padding: 2rem;
            border-radius: 12px;
            text-align: center;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            border: 2px solid transparent;
        }

        .feature-card:hover {
            border-color: var(--primary);
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
        }

        .feature-icon {
            font-size: 3rem;
            color: var(--primary);
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .feature-card h3 {
            color: var(--gray-dark);
            margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
        }

        .feature-card p {
            color: var(--gray);
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }

        .timeline {
            position: relative;
            padding: 2rem 0;
        }

        .timeline-item {
            display: flex;
            gap: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            position: relative;
        }

        .timeline-item:before {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            left: 31px;
            top: 50px;
            bottom: -50px;
            width: 2px;
            background: var(--light);
        }

        .timeline-item:last-child:before { display: none; }

        .timeline-dot {
            width: 64px;
            height: 64px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary) 0%, var(--primary-dark) 100%);
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: white;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            flex-shrink: 0;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
        }

        .timeline-content { padding-top: 0.75rem; }

        .timeline-content h3 {
            color: var(--gray-dark);
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .timeline-content p {
            color: var(--gray);
            margin: 0;
        }

        .tech-stack {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(150px, 1fr));
            gap: 1rem;
            margin-top: 1.5rem;
        }

        .tech-badge {
            background: var(--light);
            padding: 1rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-align: center;
            border: 2px solid transparent;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .tech-badge:hover {
            border-color: var(--primary);
            background: white;
        }

        .tech-badge strong {
            display: block;
            color: var(--gray-dark);
            margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
        }

        .tech-badge small { color: var(--gray); }

        .comparison-box {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .comparison-item {
            background: var(--lighter);
            padding: 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        .comparison-item h3 {
            color: var(--gray-dark);
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--light);
            padding-bottom: 0.75rem;
        }

        .difference {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 0.75rem 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }

        .difference:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

        .difference-label {
            color: var(--gray);
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .difference-value {
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--primary);
        }

        .empty-state {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 3rem 1rem;
            color: var(--gray);
        }

        .empty-state i {
            font-size: 3rem;
            color: var(--light);
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .empty-state p { margin: 0; }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .container { padding: 1rem; }
            section { padding: 1.5rem; }
            .header-content {
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 1rem;
                padding: 1rem;
            }
            nav {
                flex-direction: column;
                border-top: none;
            }
            .nav-button {
                min-width: 100%;
                border-bottom: none;
                border-right: 3px solid transparent;
            }
            .nav-button.active {
                border-right-color: white;
                border-bottom: none;
            }
            .dashboard-grid,
            .form-group-row,
            .comparison-box {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 640px) {
            .form-group-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div class="header-content">
            <div class="logo">
                <i class="fas fa-shopping-cart"></i>
                <span>Smart Market</span>
            </div>
            <div class="status-sync">
                <span class="dot"></span>
                <span>Sincronizando em tempo real</span>
            </div>
        </div>

        <nav>
            <button class="nav-button active" onclick="showSection('dashboard', this)">
                <i class="fas fa-tachometer-alt"></i> Dashboard
            </button>
            <button class="nav-button" onclick="showSection('registrar', this)">
                <i class="fas fa-plus-circle"></i> Registrar
            </button>
            <button class="nav-button" onclick="showSection('historico', this)">
                <i class="fas fa-history"></i> Histórico
            </button>
            <button class="nav-button" onclick="showSection('comparar', this)">
                <i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i> Comparar
            </button>
            <button class="nav-button" onclick="showSection('analisar', this)">
                <i class="fas fa-chart-pie"></i> Análise
            </button>
            <button class="nav-button" onclick="showSection('sobre', this)">
                <i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i> Sobre
            </button>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <div class="container">
        <section id="dashboard" class="active">
            <h2><i class="fas fa-tachometer-alt"></i> Dashboard</h2>

            <div class="dashboard-grid">
                <div class="dashboard-card">
                    <h3>Total de Compras</h3>
                    <p class="metric-value" id="totalCompras">0</p>
                    <p class="metric-label">Compras registradas</p>
                </div>
                <div class="dashboard-card">
                    <h3>Gasto Total</h3>
                    <p class="metric-value" id="totalGasto">R$ 0,00</p>
                    <p class="metric-label">Valor acumulado</p>
                </div>
                <div class="dashboard-card">
                    <h3>Média por Compra</h3>
                    <p class="metric-value" id="mediaTicket">R$ 0,00</p>
                    <p class="metric-label">Ticket médio</p>
                </div>
                <div class="dashboard-card">
                    <h3>Categoria Destaque</h3>
                    <p class="metric-value" id="topCategoria">—</p>
                    <p class="metric-label">Maior gasto</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="dashboard-grid">
                <div class="card">
                    <h3>Gasto por Categoria</h3>
                    <div class="chart-container">
                        <canvas id="categoriaChart"></canvas>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <h3>Evolução de Compras</h3>
                    <div class="chart-container">
                        <canvas id="comparacaoChart"></canvas>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="card">
                    <h3>Distribuição por Categoria</h3>
                    <div class="chart-container">
                        <canvas id="participacaoChart"></canvas>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="registrar">
            <h2><i class="fas fa-receipt"></i> Registrar Nova Compra</h2>

            <form id="compraForm">
                <div class="form-group-row">
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="mercado"><i class="fas fa-store"></i> Mercado</label>
                        <input type="text" id="mercado" placeholder="Ex: Carrefour, Pão de Açúcar..." required />
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="data"><i class="fas fa-calendar-alt"></i> Data</label>
                        <input type="date" id="data" required />
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="hora"><i class="fas fa-clock"></i> Hora</label>
                    <input type="time" id="hora" required />
                </div>

                <div class="items-container">
                    <h3><i class="fas fa-list"></i> Itens da Compra</h3>
                    <div id="itens"></div>
                </div>

                <div class="form-group">
                    <button type="button" class="btn-secondary" onclick="addItem()">
                        <i class="fas fa-plus"></i> Adicionar Item
                    </button>
                </div>

                <button type="submit" class="btn-primary">
                    <i class="fas fa-save"></i> Salvar Compra
                </button>
            </form>
        </section>

        <section id="historico">
            <h2><i class="fas fa-history"></i> Histórico de Compras</h2>
            <div id="historicoContainer">
                <div class="empty-state">
                    <i class="fas fa-inbox"></i>
                    <p>Nenhuma compra registrada ainda</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="comparar">
            <h2><i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i> Comparar Compras</h2>
            <p>Selecione duas compras para comparar seus totais e variações.</p>

            <div class="form-group-row">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="compra1"><i class="fas fa-receipt"></i> Primeira Compra</label>
                    <select id="compra1">
                        <option value="">Selecione uma compra</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="compra2"><i class="fas fa-receipt"></i> Segunda Compra</label>
                    <select id="compra2">
                        <option value="">Selecione uma compra</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
            </div>

            <button onclick="compararCompras()" class="btn-primary">
                <i class="fas fa-balance-scale"></i> Comparar
            </button>

            <div id="resultadoComparacao" style="margin-top: 2rem;"></div>
        </section>

        <section id="analisar">
            <h2><i class="fas fa-chart-pie"></i> Análise de Consumo</h2>
            <p>Visualize as categorias com maior gasto acumulado.</p>

            <div id="analiseContainer">
                <div class="empty-state">
                    <i class="fas fa-chart-pie"></i>
                    <p>Sem dados para análise</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="sobre">
            <div class="about-hero">
                <h1><i class="fas fa-rocket"></i> Smart Market</h1>
                <p>Controle inteligente e profissional das suas compras de supermercado com sincronização em tempo real</p>
            </div>

            <h2 style="border-top: 2px solid var(--light); padding-top: 2rem;">
                <i class="fas fa-lightbulb"></i> O Projeto
            </h2>
            <p>
                Smart Market é uma aplicação web moderna desenvolvida para ajudar você a gerenciar suas compras de supermercado
                de forma inteligente e eficiente. A plataforma oferece ferramentas poderosas para registrar, analisar e comparar compras,
                ajudando você a entender seus padrões de gasto.
            </p>

            <h2 style="margin-top: 2rem;"><i class="fas fa-star"></i> Funcionalidades Principais</h2>

            <div class="features-grid">
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-icon"><i class="fas fa-receipt"></i></div>
                    <h3>Registrar Compras</h3>
                    <p>Registre todas as suas compras com detalhes de mercado, data, hora e itens</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-icon"><i class="fas fa-tachometer-alt"></i></div>
                    <h3>Dashboard Interativo</h3>
                    <p>Visualize estatísticas em tempo real sobre seus gastos</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-icon"><i class="fas fa-history"></i></div>
                    <h3>Histórico Completo</h3>
                    <p>Acesse todo o histórico de compras e navegue pelos detalhes</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-icon"><i class="fas fa-balance-scale"></i></div>
                    <h3>Comparar Compras</h3>
                    <p>Compare duas compras para entender variações de preço</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-icon"><i class="fas fa-chart-pie"></i></div>
                    <h3>Análise de Categorias</h3>
